name: Musical Overture
tag_list: music, musicians, young-musicians, video-sharing, aspiring-musicians, online-portfolio, virtual-performance-hall, what-color-is-your-curtain-
overview:
Musical Overture is an online community of aspiring musicians showcasing their talents before the world and the watchful eyes of conservatory and university recruiters.

It is a place where young musicians find community, performance experience, helpful instruction, and a platform from which they can enter the next stage of their training. Think performance venue. Think community of musicians searching to find their path to a lifetime of making music. Think resource for developing musical skills. Think collection of the brightest musical talent in the world. Musical Overture is all of these things….and more.

Join us at Musical Overture. It costs nothing to become a member. Browse the videos posted by the many talented musicians from around the world. Choose your favorites and follow their careers. Allow them to enrich your life through music.
